    <div id="res828499273" class="bucketwrap bookedition">
      <h6><a href="https://www.npr.org/books/titles/828499236/see-you-on-sunday-a-cookbook-for-family-and-friends">See You on Sunday</a></h6>
   <p>A Cookbook for Family and Friends</p>   <p class="author">by <a href="https://www.npr.org/books/authors/165493502/sam-sifton"><span>Sam Sifton</span></a>, <a href="https://www.npr.org/books/authors/828499246/david-malosh"><span>David Malosh</span></a> and <a href="https://www.npr.org/books/authors/828499252/simon-andrews"><span>Simon Andrews</span></a></p>   <div class="bookinfo">
            <p>Hardcover, 368 pages <span class="pipe">|</span></p>      <a href="#" class="purchase" data-metrics='{"category":"Ecommerce","action":"Click purchase book"}' >purchase</a>      <div class="ecommercepop">
